# =============================================================================
# File: /opt/ansible-k3s-cluster/README.cluster-roles
# =============================================================================
# Purpose:
#   Document the operational roles within the cluster automation framework.
#   This ensures clear separation of duties and prevents privilege overlap.
#
# Roles:
#
#   Builder:
#     - Owns kernel source tree
#     - Runs distributed builds
#     - Verifies artifacts
#
#   Ansible:
#     - Deploys kernels
#     - Manages distccd on nodes
#     - Performs cluster-wide diagnostics
#
#   Worker Nodes:
#     - Run distccd
#     - Run k3s workloads
#     - Receive kernel artifacts
#
# Notes:
#   - This file defines the authoritative role model for the cluster.
# =============================================================================
